data.description: Corner lot in River Landing! Like-new home features blinds throughout, full sprinkler system and open floor plan. Kitchen features an island and stainless appliances with a gas stove plus adjoining breakfast/dining space. Owner’s retreat includes a walk-in closet and private bath that features separate shower, soaking tub and double vanity. Prepped and ready for a home generator! Fully fenced back yard with single and double gates! Beautiful maintained flat lawn with a covered back patio. This community features access to incredible amenities clubhouse, swimming pool, fitness center, playground, basketball and tennis court and much more! Mins to arsenal, 565, shopping, TN river and more!
